      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/a/cc9497/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2020-12-08T01:45:48.636Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Was doing a ride tonight and HR just left ,changed battery and though maybe something else stole the signal but Wahoo bolt showed it<br>\nLooked under sensors in the app and it appears it views both my 4iiii Precision and my Viiiiva as power to the H3<br>\niPhone Xr<br>\nUnloaded app and reloaded,turned BT off and on same results<br>\nH3 worked fine with whatever signal it got</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/1X/a28758860c1769be7281d3cebf982f7ec02ef868.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/a28758860c1769be7281d3cebf982f7ec02ef868\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/a28758860c1769be7281d3cebf982f7ec02ef868_2_231x500.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"nbNkhUW9SmwIBwKsffi3A4mTYwg\" width=\"231\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/a28758860c1769be7281d3cebf982f7ec02ef868_2_231x500.jpeg, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/a28758860c1769be7281d3cebf982f7ec02ef868_2_346x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/a28758860c1769be7281d3cebf982f7ec02ef868_2_462x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/a28758860c1769be7281d3cebf982f7ec02ef868_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">828\u00d71792 137 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
