      "created_at": "2020-12-08T06:42:32.516Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I\u2019m not really sure about this, but if I remember correctly, your Viiiva HRM can receive Ant+ channels from your power sources.</p>\n<p>I suspect that this is what\u2019s happening here - I guess that if you choose the Viiiva, it will record both power and HRM.</p>\n<p>You would want to make sure that the power it captures is from your Hammer indoors and your Precission outdoors.</p>\n<p>Or, only from your Precission, to ensure compatibility between in- and outdoors.</p>",
