      "created_at": "2020-12-08T13:24:11.149Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Yes, it was an early ant+ BT bridge setup but my Precision PM is also BT as is the H3 and I have yet to understand how to prioritize them other than PowerMatch the Precision which I have done, the HR strap dropped signal so I unpaired from everything then changed battery (showing 48% in the 4iiii app) and resynched and it came up as power for some reason. then foolishly discarded the warmup workout which may have been valuable from a diagnostic standpoint for Alex and his team\u2026</p>",
