      "created_at": "2020-12-08T18:42:02.884Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I had only turned on the WaHoo after the HR went away in the app to see if it was the HR strap or the app it as worked before with both units on (and both receiving HR data )<br>\nI can capture all the info on my Wahoo and upload that to Strava until your developer gets to it, not a major issue as the app still controls the trainer ERG which is my priority</p>\n<p>Cyclopaat, In the 4iiii app you have to pair your Ant+ to the HRM for it to bridge , I have cleared that. it should just be a BT HRM at this point.</p>\n<p>Just keeping up with my Motto :  Always an Adventure <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=9\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\"> <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/joy.png?v=9\" title=\":joy:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":joy:\"></p>",
